'''Heroku'''是一个支持多种[[编程语言|编程语言]]的云[[平台即服务|平台即服务]]。在2010年被[[Salesforce.com|Salesforce.com]]收购。Heroku作为最元祖的[[云端计算|云平台]]之一<ref>{{Citation | title = Salesforce signs definitive agreement to acquire Heroku | url = http://news.heroku.com/news_releases/salesforcecom-signs-definitive-agreement-to-acquire-heroku | publisher = Heroku | type = news release | accessdate = 2014-06-02 | archive-date = 2014-07-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140726162859/http://news.heroku.com/news_releases/salesforcecom-signs-definitive-agreement-to-acquire-heroku | dead-url = no }}</ref>，从[[2007年6月|2007年6月]]起开发，当时它仅支持[[Ruby|Ruby]]，但后来增加了对[[Java|Java]]、[[Node.js|Node.js]]、[[Scala|Scala]]、[[Clojure|Clojure]]、[[Python|Python]]以及（未记录在正式文件上）[[PHP|PHP]]和[[Perl|Perl]]的支持。基础操作系统是[[Debian|Debian]]，在最新的技術堆栈则是基于Debian的[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Stacks|publisher=Heroku Dev Center|url=https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/stack|accessdate=May 15, 2012|archive-date=2014-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629215157/https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/stack|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
James Lindenbaum、Adam Wiggins和Orion Henry建立了Heroku，用于支持兼容[[Rack_(web_server_interface)|Rack]]的项目。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.techcrunch.com/2008/05/08/ruby-on-rails-startup-heroku-gets-3-million | date = 2008-05-08 | title = Ruby on Rails Startup Heroku Gets $3 Million | publisher = Tech Crunch | accessdate = 2014-06-02 | archive-date = 2014-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140912015327/http://techcrunch.com/2008/05/08/ruby-on-rails-startup-heroku-gets-3-million/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[2009年10月|2009年10月]]，Byron Sebastian作为CEO加入了Heroku。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://venturebeat.com/2009/10/14/sourcelabs-byron-sebastian-joins-heroku-as-ceo | date = 2009-10-14 | title = SourceLabs' Byron Sebastian Joins Heroku as CEO | publisher = Venture Beat | accessdate = 2014-06-02 | archive-date = 2015-04-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150408132741/http://venturebeat.com/2009/10/14/sourcelabs-byron-sebastian-joins-heroku-as-ceo/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>2010年12月8日，Heroku成Salesforce.com完全控股的子公司。

2011年6月12日，[[Ruby|Ruby]]的首席设计师[[松本行弘|松本行弘]]加盟该公司，担任Ruby的首席架构师。<ref>{{Citation | type = weblog | url = http://blog.heroku.com/archives/2011/7/12/matz_joins_heroku/ | title = Matz joins Heroku | date = 2011-07-12 | publisher = Heroku | accessdate = 2014-06-02 | archive-date = 2012-10-31 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6Bp5owViA?url=http://blog.heroku.com/archives/2011/7/12/matz_joins_heroku/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>当月，Heroku加入了[[Node.js|Node.js]]和[[Clojure|Clojure]]的支持。

2011年9月15日，Heroku和[[Facebook|Facebook]]合作。<ref>{{Citation | url = http://developers.facebook.com/blog/post/558/ | contribution = Facebook and Heroku: an even easier way to get started | publisher = Facebook | title = Developers | type = weblog | accessdate = 2014-06-02 | archive-date = 2012-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121003155617/https://developers.facebook.com/blog/post/558/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>现在，除了基础的[[PostgreSQL|PostgreSQL]]<ref>{{Citation | url = https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/database | contribution = Database | title = Dev Centre | publisher = Heroku | accessdate = 2012-05-03 | quote = Heroku offers you the choice of running on a shared or dedicated database package. The shared plan is suitable for development and staging applications. It runs Postgres 8.3. The dedicated plans are suitable for production scale applications. In addition, the dedicated databases offer a number of advantages, including direct access (via psql or any native postgres library), stored procedures, and Postgres 9 support. | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120324150743/http://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/database | archivedate = 2012-03-24 }}</ref>之外，Heroku还支持[[Cloudant|Cloudant]]、[[Couchbase_Server|Couchbase Server]]、[[MongoDB|MongoDB]]和[[Redis|Redis]]<ref>{{Citation | url = http://blog.heroku.com/archives/2010/7/20/nosql/ | publisher = Heroku | date = 2010-07-20 | title = NoSQL, Heroku, and You | type = weblog | accessdate = 2014-06-02 | archive-date = 2012-10-31 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6Bp5sncjD?url=http://blog.heroku.com/archives/2010/7/20/nosql/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，既作为平台的一部分，又作为一个独立的服务。<ref>{{Citation | url = https://postgres.heroku.com/ | publisher = Heroku | title = SQL Database-as-a-Service: the largest and most reliable Postgres service in the world | accessdate = 2012-05-03 | quote = A powerful, reliable, and durable open-source SQL-compliant database, PostgreSQL is the datastore of choice for serious applications. Now it is available in seconds with a single click. Never worry about servers. Never worry about config files. Never worry about patches. Simply focus on your data. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120509091123/https://postgres.heroku.com/ | archive-date = 2012-05-09 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>在Heroku服务器上运行的应用程序使用Heroku的[[DNS|DNS]]服务器连接至应用程序的域名（通常为“应用程序名.herokuapp.com”）。每个应用程序容器（称为dyno）跨越由多个服务器组成的“dyno grid”。Heroku的[[Git|Git]]服务器处理来自授权用户的应用程序库推送请求。<ref>[http://www.quora.com/Scalability/How-does-Heroku-work Scalability: How does Heroku work?]</ref>

{{le|2012年北美雷雨|June_2012_North_American_derecho}}导致很多Heroku托管的应用脱机，服务持续中断近24小时。<ref>{{cite news|last=Ludwig|first=Sear|title=Amazon cloud outage takes down Netflix, Instagram, Pinterest, & more|url=http://venturebeat.com/2012/06/29/amazon-outage-netflix-instagram-pinterest/|accessdate=8 July 2012|newspaper=VentureBeat|date=June 29, 2012|archive-date=2014-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605052247/http://venturebeat.com/2012/06/29/amazon-outage-netflix-instagram-pinterest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

